---
title: Hot Honey Peach Pork Chops with Rice & Lemony Roasted Veggies
description: Sugar and spice and everything nice; that’s what these hot honey peach pork chops are made of! Mike’s Hot Honey is swirled with peach jam, butter, and lemon juice for a sticky-sweet glaze for pork. Roasted carrots and zucchini are tossed with lemon zest and a pinch of chili flakes, then paired with buttery rice on the side. Spicy-sweet and perfectly balanced—these pork chops will leave you simply s(peach)less!
